e^{-\lambda z}
F_Z(z)=\Pr(Z\le z)=\int_0^z \lambda e^{-\lambda x}\,dx+ \int_1^{1+z} \lambda e^{-\lambda x}\,dx +   \int_2^{2+z} \lambda e^{-\lambda x}\,dx + \cdots.
f_Z(z)=\lambda\left( e^{-\lambda z}+  e^{-\lambda (1+z)}+ e^{-\lambda (2+z)}+e^{-\lambda (2+z)}+\cdots                            \right).
